# systemd-sysusers spec for turf-tracker.
#
# Loaded by `systemd-sysusers --replace=/usr/lib/sysusers.d/<name>.conf`
# during RPM %pre (via the %sysusers_create_package macro) — creates
# the user/group declaratively. Format:
#
#   Type  Name          ID  GECOS                          Home                    Shell
u         turf-tracker  -   "turf-tracker service account" /var/lib/turf-tracker   /sbin/nologin
